                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The waveriders conjure a cresting wave beneath their feet and use it ride down their enemies. The waveriders Stride up to double their Speed and can move through the spaces of Medium or smaller creatures or troops composed of Medium or smaller creatures. Creatures in the path of the waveriders take @Damage[(1d8+6)[bludgeoning]] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:30|basic] save).</p>"
